{"type":"message","id":"9b8f19e8","parentId":"5341b5a9","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:42:17.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to follow the session startup sequence as instructed. Let me read the required files:\n1. SOUL.md - who I am\n2. USER.md - who I'm helping\n3. memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) - recent context\n4. MEMORY.md - long-term memory (only in main session)\n\nLet me start reading these files.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a28091d55e5941b691ac3e6b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_389af815f24845ebbd482612","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5f90638879984e2b89260fac","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/memory/2026-03-10.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3ff9539e22a34d24bab3a83e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/memory/2026-03-09.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1099599994084bfd98866b89","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773106933039}}
{"type":"message","id":"d1d1948d","parentId":"9b8f19e8","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:42:17.448Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a28091d55e5941b691ac3e6b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 一、核心原则\n1. **诚实第一**：不确定的内容明确说明“不知道”，不编造信息。\n2. **效率优先**：能一步完成的操作不分步执行，沟通与执行不啰嗦。\n3. **尊重用户**：认真倾听用户需求，不擅自替用户做出决策。\n\n## 二、行为准则\n- 被用户纠正错误时，立即道歉并修正，同时将问题记录至`LEARNINGS.md`文件。\n- 处理复杂任务时，先拆解具体步骤，与用户确认后再开展执行。\n- 涉及删除、修改等敏感操作时，必须向用户进行二次确认，确认后再操作。\n\n## 三、回复风格\n- 中文环境下，统一使用中文进行回复。\n- 解答技术问题：保持逻辑清晰、内容结构化呈现。\n- 日常闲聊沟通：语气轻松，带有温度，贴合交流场景。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773106937445}}
{"type":"message","id":"473d110b","parentId":"d1d1948d","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:42:17.452Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_389af815f24845ebbd482612","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n## 基本信息\n- **称呼**：老板\n- **职业**：股民\n- **技术背景**：不懂技术的领导\n\n## 偏好设置\n- 文档输出：Markdown格式，方便复制\n- 沟通方式：直说重点，不需要客套话 \n\n## Context\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773106937450}}
{"type":"message","id":"884e5e6c","parentId":"473d110b","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:42:17.456Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5f90638879984e2b89260fac","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-10 股票监控记录\n\n## 检查时间\n2026-03-10 07:49 AM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\n## 预警结果\n✅ 已发送预警通知到飞书\n\n### 触发预警股票 (3 只)\n1. **920876.BJ 慧为智能**: +19.32% (¥32.49, +¥5.26) - 上涨>5%\n2. **601857.SH 中国石油**: +5.04% (¥12.92, +¥0.62) - 上涨>5% + 个股规则 (涨幅>2%)\n3. **000852.SZ 石化机械**: -3.33% (¥8.41, -¥0.29) - 下跌>3%\n\n### 未触发预警股票\n- 601808.SH 中海油服: +2.51%\n- 600256.SH 广汇能源: +4.26%\n- 600547.SH 山东黄金: +1.98%\n- 600583.SH 海油工程: -0.53%\n- 600988.SH 赤峰黄金: +1.53%\n- 601069.SH 西部黄金: +3.40%\n- 000975.SZ 银泰黄金: +3.61%\n- 002716.SZ 金贵银业: -0.81%\n- 601899.SH 紫金矿业: -1.89%\n- 688111.SH 金山办公: -1.70%\n- AAPL 苹果: +0.94%\n- 9866.HK 蔚来-SW: 无数据\n\n---\n数据来源：Tushare Pro\n数据日期：2026-03-09 (最新交易日)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773106937454}}
