{"type":"message","id":"0368010a","parentId":"d02d4d3d","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:44:00.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我了解了 tushare 的使用方式。现在我需要获取这些股票的实时数据。根据 TOOLS.md 的要求，进行涨跌分析时要获取实时数据，参考实时分钟和实时日线接口。\n\n让我创建一个 Python 脚本来获取这些股票的实时行情数据。我需要：\n1. 使用 tushare 获取实时日线数据\n2. 格式化输出结果\n\n根据 watchlist.txt，我有 15 只股票，包括 A 股、港股和美股。让我编写一个脚本来获取这些数据。\n\n股票代码需要转换为 tushare 格式：\n- 601857 -> 601857.SH (中国石油)\n- 601808 -> 601808.SH (中海油服)\n- 600256 -> 600256.SH (广汇能源)\n- 600583 -> 600583.SH (海油工程)\n- 000852 -> 000852.SZ (石化机械)\n- 600547 -> 600547.SH (山东黄金)\n- 601069 -> 601069.SH (西部黄金)\n- 600988 -> 600988.SH (赤峰黄金)\n- 000975 -> 000975.SZ (银泰黄金)\n- 002716 -> 002716.SZ (金贵银业)\n- 601899 -> 601899.SH (紫金矿业)\n- 9866.HK -> 9866.HK (蔚来-SW)\n- AAPL -> AAPL (苹果)\n- 920876 -> 920876.BJ (慧为智能)\n- 688111 -> 688111.SH (金山办公)\n\n让我创建一个脚本来获取实时日线数据。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7f5a73fccb3f4f01aca6e796","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 初始化\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\nts.set_token(token)\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 股票代码列表 (ts_code 格式)\nstocks = [\n    '601857.SH', '601808.SH', '600256.SH', '600583.SH', '000852.SZ',\n    '600547.SH', '601069.SH', '600988.SH', '000975.SZ', '002716.SZ',\n    '601899.SH', '9866.HK', 'AAPL', '920876.BJ', '688111.SH'\n]\n\n# 获取实时日线数据\nresults = []\nfor code in stocks:\n    try:\n        # 获取日线数据\n        df = pro.daily(ts_code=code, start_date=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d'), \n                       end_date=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d'))\n        if df.empty:\n            # 尝试获取最近一天的数据\n            df = pro.daily(ts_code=code, start_date='20260309', end_date='20260310')\n        \n        if not df.empty:\n            row = df.iloc[0]\n            results.append({\n                'code': code,\n                'name': '',\n                'price': row.get('close', 0),\n                'change': row.get('pct_chg', 0),\n                'pre_close': row.get('pre_close', 0)\n            })\n    except Exception as e:\n        results.append({\n            'code': code,\n            'name': '',\n            'price': 0,\n            'change': 0,\n            'pre_close': 0,\n            'error': str(e)\n        })\n\n# 输出结果\nfor r in results:\n    print(f\"{r['code']}: price={r['price']}, change={r['change']:.2f}%, pre_close={r['pre_close']}\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773107029412}}
