{"type":"message","id":"9e686e02","parentId":"76ed77df","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:51:10.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求查看股票的分钟级实时数据。根据 tushare skill 的文档，我需要找到正确的分钟数据接口。\n\n从技能文档中，我看到有这些相关接口：\n- 实时分钟：https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=374 - 获取全 A 股票实时分钟数据，包括 1~60min\n- 历史分钟：获取 A 股分钟数据，支持 1min/5min/15min/30min/60min 行情\n\n但是我之前尝试使用 `stk_min` 接口时报错\"请指定正确的接口名\"。\n\n让我查看一下正确的接口名称。根据文档 doc_id=374，实时分钟接口应该是 `stk_min` 或者可能是其他名称。\n\n让我尝试使用正确的接口名来获取分钟级数据。根据 tushare 文档，实时分钟接口可能是：\n- `stk_min` - 但之前报错\n- 或者需要通过 HTTP API 访问\n\n让我尝试其他方式获取实时分钟数据。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7707250077024544b8251bc3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 初始化\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\nts.set_token(token)\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 股票代码列表\nstocks = [\n    {'ts_code': '601857.SH', 'name': '中国石油'},\n    {'ts_code': '601808.SH', 'name': '中海油服'},\n    {'ts_code': '600256.SH', 'name': '广汇能源'},\n    {'ts_code': '000852.SZ', 'name': '石化机械'},\n    {'ts_code': '600547.SH', 'name': '山东黄金'},\n    {'ts_code': '601069.SH', 'name': '西部黄金'},\n    {'ts_code': '600988.SH', 'name': '赤峰黄金'},\n    {'ts_code': '000975.SZ', 'name': '银泰黄金'},\n    {'ts_code': '601899.SH', 'name': '紫金矿业'},\n    {'ts_code': '920876.BJ', 'name': '慧为智能'},\n    {'ts_code': '688111.SH', 'name': '金山办公'},\n]\n\nprint(\"=== 尝试获取分钟级数据 ===\")\nprint(f\"当前时间：{datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\")\n\n# 尝试不同的分钟数据接口\nfor stock in stocks[:5]:  # 先测试 5 只\n    try:\n        # 尝试历史分钟接口 (doc_id=374)\n        df = pro.stk_min(ts_code=stock['ts_code'], freq='1min', start_date=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d'), \n                         end_date=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d%H%M'))\n        if not df.empty:\n            print(f\"\\n{stock['name']} ({stock['ts_code']}): 获取到 {len(df)} 条记录\")\n            print(df[['trade_time', 'price', 'pct_chg']].tail(3))\n        else:\n            print(f\"{stock['name']}: 无数据\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"{stock['name']}: 错误 - {str(e)[:100]}\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773107445525}}
