{"type":"message","id":"a0d90543","parentId":"484bf3fd","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:51:19.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"tushare 的 stk_min 接口名不对。让我查看一下正确的接口名称。根据 tushare 文档，分钟数据接口可能是 `min` 或者其他名称。让我尝试其他可能的接口名。\n\n根据文档 https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=374，实时分钟接口应该是通过 HTTP API 访问的。让我尝试使用正确的接口名。\n\n可能的接口名：\n- `stk_min` - 已尝试，报错\n- `min` - 试试看\n- `realtime_min` - 试试看\n\n或者我需要使用 HTTP API 方式来获取。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4ffb6e441e1f4688a7e6e64e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\nimport requests\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 初始化\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\n\n# 尝试使用 HTTP API 获取分钟数据\n# 参考文档：https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=374\n\nstocks = [\n    {'ts_code': '601857.SH', 'name': '中国石油'},\n    {'ts_code': '601808.SH', 'name': '中海油服'},\n    {'ts_code': '000852.SZ', 'name': '石化机械'},\n    {'ts_code': '600547.SH', 'name': '山东黄金'},\n    {'ts_code': '920876.BJ', 'name': '慧为智能'},\n]\n\nprint(\"=== 使用 HTTP API 获取分钟数据 ===\")\n\nfor stock in stocks:\n    try:\n        # 构建 HTTP 请求\n        url = \"http://api.tushare.pro\"\n        headers = {\"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"}\n        \n        # 分钟数据接口\n        data = {\n            \"api_name\": \"stk_min\",\n            \"token\": token,\n            \"params\": {\n                \"ts_code\": stock['ts_code'],\n                \"freq\": \"1min\",\n                \"asset\": \"E\"\n            }\n        }\n        \n        response = requests.post(url, json=data, headers=headers, timeout=10)\n        result = response.json()\n        \n        if result.get('code') == 0:\n            df = result.get('data', {}).get('items', [])\n            fields = result.get('data', {}).get('fields', [])\n            print(f\"\\n{stock['name']} ({stock['ts_code']}): 获取到 {len(df)} 条记录\")\n            if df and fields:\n                # 显示最后 3 条\n                for row in df[-3:]:\n                    print(f\"  时间：{row[fields.index('trade_time')] if 'trade_time' in fields else 'N/A'}, \"\n                          f\"价格：{row[fields.index('price')] if 'price' in fields else 'N/A'}\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"{stock['name']}: API 错误 - {result.get('msg', 'Unknown error')}\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"{stock['name']}: 错误 - {str(e)[:100]}\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773107471697}}
